<section id="contact" class="py-16 sm:py-20">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
		<div class="grid gap-3">
			<h2 class="reveal text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-950 dark:text-white" data-reveal>Kontak</h2>
			<p class="reveal max-w-[78ch] text-pretty text-base leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300" data-reveal>
				Punya ide, butuh bantuan UI, atau mau diskusi project? Kirim brief singkat — saya respon cepat.
			</p>
		</div>

			<div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-2">
				<div class="card reveal p-6" data-reveal>
					<div class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-950 dark:text-white">Ceritain kebutuhanmu</div>
					<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
						Kirim ringkas: tujuan, fitur utama, referensi desain, dan deadline. Saya balas dengan breakdown scope, estimasi, dan langkah next.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						<a class="btn-primary" href="mailto:dimasputranugrh@gmail.com">Email Saya</a>
						<a class="btn-ghost" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dimasputranugrh/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
					</div>
				<div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 border-t border-zinc-950/10 pt-5 dark:border-white/10">
					<div>
						<div class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">Lokasi</div>
						<div class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-950 dark:text-white">Indonesia</div>
					</div>
					<div>
						<div class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">Ketersediaan</div>
						<div class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-950 dark:text-white">Freelance</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<form class="card reveal grid gap-3 p-6 sm:grid-cols-2" name="contact" method="POST" action="/#contact" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" data-reveal>
				<input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
				<label class="hidden">
					<span>Don’t fill this out if you’re human:</span>
					<input name="bot-field" />
				</label>
				<label class="grid gap-2">
					<span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">Nama</span>
					<input
						class="h-11 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-950/10 bg-white/70 px-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 shadow-sm outline-none transition focus:border-zinc-950/30 focus:bg-white dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-white dark:focus:border-white/25 dark:focus:bg-white/10"
						name="name"
						placeholder="Nama kamu"
						autocomplete="name"
					/>
				</label>
				<label class="grid gap-2">
					<span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">Email</span>
					<input
						class="h-11 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-950/10 bg-white/70 px-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 shadow-sm outline-none transition focus:border-zinc-950/30 focus:bg-white dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-white dark:focus:border-white/25 dark:focus:bg-white/10"
						name="email"
						placeholder="email@domain.com"
						autocomplete="email"
					/>
				</label>
				<label class="grid gap-2 sm:col-span-2">
					<span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">Pesan</span>
					<textarea
						class="min-h-[140px] rounded-2xl border border-zinc-950/10 bg-white/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 shadow-sm outline-none transition focus:border-zinc-950/30 focus:bg-white dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:text-white dark:focus:border-white/25 dark:focus:bg-white/10"
						name="message"
						rows="5"
						placeholder="Ceritain projectmu..."
					></textarea>
				</label>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3 sm:col-span-2">
					<button class="btn-primary" type="submit">Kirim Pesan</button>
					<span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">Pesan akan terkirim, saya balas via email.</span>
				</div>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
